<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; line-height:1.3em; vertical-align:middle;">
<div style="padding-top:0.25em; text-align:left; font-style:90%;"><b>Notes</b><br />
Fellow of the <a href="/wiki/Royal_Society" title="Royal Society">Royal Society</a><br />
Fellow of the <a href="/wiki/Royal_Society_of_Literature" title="Royal Society of Literature">Royal Society of Literature</a></div>
